<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.js"></script>
<script>
$(document).ready(function () {
$("button").click(function () {
var i=1;
do{
$("p:odd").fadeToggle();
i++;
if(i%2==0){
$("p:even").fadeToggle();}
}
while(i<3000)
$("p:odd").hide();
});
});
</script>
</head>
<body>
<br><br><button>Click me</button>

<p style="display:none">A night, a street, a lamp, a drugstore</p>
<p style="display:none">A meaningless and dismal light</p>
<p style="display:none">A quarter century outpours -</p>
<p style="display:none">It’s all the same. No chance to flight.</p>
<p style="display:none">You’d die and rise anew, begotten.</p>
<p style="display:none">All would repeat as ever might:</p>
<p style="display:none">The street, the icy rippled water,</p>
<p style="display:none">The store, the lamp, the lonely night.</p>

</body>
</html>
